Description_lang: While your Felguard is active, your Wild Imps and Dreadstalkers deal $s1% additional damage.

description_blz.en_US: While your Felguard is active, your Wild Imps and Dreadstalkers deal 5% additional damage.
description_blz.es_MX: Mientras tu guardia vil está activo, tus diablillos salvajes y acechadores nefastos tienen un 5% más de daño.
description_blz.pt_BR: Enquanto seu Guarda Vil estiver ativo, seus Diabretes Selvagens e Espreitadores do Medo causam 5% a mais de dano.
description_blz.de_DE: Während Eure Teufelswache aktiv ist, verursachen Eure Wildwichtel und Schreckenspirscher 5% zusätzlichen Schaden.
description_blz.en_GB: While your Felguard is active, your Wild Imps and Dreadstalkers deal 5% additional damage.
description_blz.es_ES: Mientras tu guardia vil está activo, tus diablillos salvajes y terracechadores infligen un 5% de daño extra.
description_blz.fr_FR: Quand votre gangregarde est actif, vos diablotins sauvages et vos traqueffrois infligent 5% de dégâts supplémentaires.

description_blz.ko_KR: 지옥수호병이 활성화된 동안 날뛰는 임프와 공포사냥개가 5%의 추가 피해를 입힙니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 在你的惡魔守衛存在期間，狂野小鬼和恐懼潛獵犬額外造成5%傷害。
description_blz.zh_CN: 当你的恶魔卫士激活时，你的野生小鬼和恐惧猎犬造成的伤害提高5%。
